[SN]TITLE[SN]
Epic snowball fight takes place at university in Canada

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Hundreds of students have taken part in a huge snowball fight in Vancouver in Canada.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
8 February 2017 Last updated at 08:31 GMT
Lots of snow fell in city over the weekend.
So a group of students from the University of British Columbia decided to organise a massive snowball fight!
Take a look at the snowy battle in action.
